p.d: Simon, a simple and nice librarian, meets a lawyer named Moro in a bar. Lightning strikes and after a few months, the two get married. However, a problem arises in the marriage: the lawyer does not succeed in making love with Simon. Simon is then ready to do anything just to be excited.
